  "title": "F&B Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>ob Description:</p><p><strong>WE ARE Japanese restaurant</strong></p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Serve & Delight:</strong> Ensure every guest has a memorable dining experience by serving with a smile.</li><li><strong>Cashier Duties:</strong> Handle inquiries, take orders, & process payments smoothly.</li><li><strong>Keep it Clean:</strong> Maintain the cleanliness & hygiene of the dining area, ensuring a welcoming environment.</li><li><strong>Communicate:</strong> Interact with customers in a friendly & professional way.</li><li><strong>Solve Problems:</strong> Address any customer issues or queries efficiently.</li><li><strong>Support the Team:</strong> Assist with any tasks assigned by the Outlet Manager.</li><li><strong>Working hours subject to the outlet.</strong></li><li><strong>5days/week, 50hrs/week ( OFF DAY CAN BE ON WEEKEND )</strong></li><li>Competitive hourly pay + performance bonuses + ⁠incentives!</li><li>Annual leave, Birthday leave, Family care leave</li><li>Medical & insurance coverage</li><li><strong>No experience</strong>? No problem! On-the-job training is provided!</li><li>working location : city area</li></ul><p>Job Type: Full-time</p><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>Flexible schedule</li><li>Food provided</li></ul><p><strong>Chan Wei Wen, Mervyn (Reg. No: R25149588)</strong></p><p><strong>ST Venture EmPloyment Agency (EA License No: 09C5583)</strong></p><p><strong>Please send an updated resume to stvea888@gmail.com if you are keen to apply for this position</strong></p>",
